<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q12_v7" title="PAES_Matematica_Q12_v7" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Sorteo solidario:<br />
      - Premio total obtenido: $72 000<br />
      - Compromiso de donación: 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo>
      </m:math>
      del premio total a una fundación<br />
      - Resto del premio: para el ganador<br />
      <br />
      ¿Cuánto dinero se dona a la fundación?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">1080<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El 15% de 72 000 se calcula como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,15</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;800</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, 1080 no corresponde a la donación pedida.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">10800<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El 15% de 72 000 se calcula como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,15</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;800</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, a la fundación se donan $10 800.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">7200<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El 15% de 72 000 es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,15</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;800</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como 7200 es distinto de 10 800, esa opción no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">4800<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El monto a donar es el 15% de 72 000, y ese cálculo da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,15</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;800</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces 4800 no es la cantidad que se dona.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar qué se pide</strong></p>
            <p>Se debe calcular el 15% del premio total de $72 000.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Convertir el porcentaje a número decimal</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>15</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>%</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>15</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>100</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0,15</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Multiplicar el premio total por 0,15</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0,15</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>10&#160;800</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Concluir</strong></p>
            <p>La cantidad de dinero que se dona a la fundación es $10 800.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Verificación</strong></p>
            <p>El resto para el ganador sería:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>10&#160;800</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>61&#160;200</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Así, premio donado más premio restante suman nuevamente $72 000.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>